<p><a name="Gravel"></a><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="4"><b>What about the "Gravel factor"?</b></font><p>

<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3">IN REGARDS to Dennis Kucinich being the only decent Democratic candidate ("The Kucinich factor," October 5): Hey, you guys ever hear of a fella named Mike Gravel? I guess you (like <i>The New York Times</i>, et. al.) are also somewhat selective in who you consider to be viable and genuine candidates.<br>
<b>Mike Yanasak</b>, from the Internet<p>
